title: EOS Data Analytics and Space Electric Thruster Systems demonstrate technology in orbit
summary: EOSDA, Dragonfly and Space Electric Thruster Systems (SETS) are part of the Noosphere Group, established in 2014 by international entrepreneur Max Polyakov to create an integrated space business.

title: L3Harris to develop missile-warning sensor for medium orbit constellation
summary: The U.S. Space Force awarded L3Harris technologies a $29 million contract to design a sensor payload that can track hypersonic missiles from medium Earth orbit.
